episodes.title: JUNGLE WARM-UP MIXSET
episodes.description:
JUNGLE is Manila's premiere Circuit Party on an international calibre that will feature nonstop entertainment and will make the Philiipines a tourist destination for the international circuit party community. It will feature an international DJ, outstanding live performances, unique interior design, and world class Filipino DJs. JUNGLE, a new party brand, is set to launch this December 6, 2014 (1st Saturday of the December) at the gigantic Portal Warehouse in Mandaluyong City, Metro Manila.

Join this beast of an event and experience one of the fiercest parties Manila has ever seen. An expected crowd of 5,000 boys and gurls across Asia means JUNGLE is the country's biggest party yet. It will officially brand Manila as a circuit party destination for circuit boys and gurls around Asia.

JUNGLE will introduce Sydney, Australias most sought after DJ and Drag sensation, DJ KITTY GLITTER! Plus circuit party veterans and world renowned Filipino producers/remixers/DJ's Brian Cua, Jay Santos and Toy Armada. Also introducing DJ Jeiel.

JUNGLE's production will feature a parade of dance-floor favorite tunes performed live by local theater greats, Martin Buen and Chesko Rodriguez. Plus a show stopping performance by rising new all girl group Sassy Girls. With performances also by Bed Manila's red hot Bikini Boys!

Renowned Singapore Based Architect and Former Dean of the College of Arts and Design of College of St. Benilde, Manolet Garcia is in charge of the interior and stage design.

Brought to you by Kris Nuevo Events, Bellhaus, and Bed Manila!

Join the event page at https://www.facebook.com/events/372084759623080 and our like page at https://www.facebook.com/junglecircuitparty to stay updated with the latest news and promos about JUNGLE!

Tickets are available online (www.smtickets.com), at all SM cinemas nationwide, and at Bed Manila!
